---
/**
 * InternalServices — charcoal section with 2x2 grid of peer support
 * services that SuperBenefit provides to its projects and cells.
 *
 * Four supports: people, shared infrastructure, funding support, admin and
 * paperwork. Decision-making lives inside the people offering.
 */
---

<section id="support" class="internal-services">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="services-label" data-animate="fade-up">Peer Support</span>
    <h2 class="services-heading" data-animate="fade-up">
      Internal services for projects &amp; cells
    </h2>
    <p class="services-lede" data-animate="fade-up">
      Projects here run their own work, but they share the people, tools, and
      practical support that keep things moving. Bring your own organization,
      anchor in our DAO, or pass through. Leave anytime.
    </p>
    <div class="services-accent" aria-hidden="true" data-animate="fade-up"></div>

    <div class="services-grid">
      <div class="service-item" data-animate="fade-up" style="--stagger: 0ms">
        <h3 class="service-item-heading">People to work with</h3>
        <p class="service-item-body">
          Find facilitators, contributors, and stewards to plug into your
          project. Get help with coordination, decision-making, and the
          day-to-day work of keeping a small team moving.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="service-item" data-animate="fade-up" style="--stagger: 100ms">
        <h3 class="service-item-heading">Shared infrastructure</h3>
        <p class="service-item-body">
          Use the DAO, shared tooling, and templates other projects already
          rely on. Take what you need, contribute what you build, and keep
          what you make.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="service-item" data-animate="fade-up" style="--stagger: 200ms">
        <h3 class="service-item-heading">Funding support</h3>
        <p class="service-item-body">
          Work with others on grant applications. Connect with fiscal hosts in
          the network who can move funds where they're needed. Share reporting
          approaches so no one figures it out alone.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="service-item" data-animate="fade-up" style="--stagger: 300ms">
        <h3 class="service-item-heading">Admin and paperwork</h3>
        <p class="service-item-body">
          Use our DAO and existing entity arrangements when you need them. We
          help with the admin, filings, and coordination that keep a project
          running.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="services-footer" data-animate="fade-up">
      <a href="/support" class="services-cta">
        See peer support details
        <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M5 12h14"></path><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"></polyline>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </footer>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .internal-services {
    background: var(--color-charcoal);
    padding-block: var(--space-xl) var(--space-2xl);
    position: relative;
  }

  /* ===== Label ===== */
  .services-label {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    color: var(--color-orange);
    margin-block-end: var(--space-sm);
  }

  /* ===== Heading ===== */
  .services-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    color: var(--color-cream);
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-block-end: var(--space-lg);
  }

  /* ===== Lede ===== */
  .services-lede {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-cream);
    opacity: 0.75;
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 620px;
    margin-block-end: var(--space-xl);
  }

  /* ===== Accent bar (MissionStatement pattern) ===== */
  .services-accent {
    width: 48px;
    height: 3px;
    background: var(--color-orange);
    border-radius: 2px;
    opacity: 0.5;
    margin-block-end: var(--space-xl);
  }

  /* ===== 2x2 services grid ===== */
  .services-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-xl) var(--space-lg);
    align-items: start;
  }

  /* ===== Service item ===== */
  .service-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .service-item-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--color-cream);
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .service-item-body {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-cream);
    opacity: 0.6;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* ===== Stagger animation delay ===== */
  .service-item[data-animate] {
    animation-delay: var(--stagger);
  }

  /* ===== Footer CTA ===== */
  .services-footer {
    margin-block-start: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .services-cta {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5em;
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-orange);
    text-decoration: none;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    transition: opacity var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .services-cta:hover {
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  /* ===== Responsive ===== */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .services-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
